260
00:26:06,317 --> 00:26:08,027
Not so great, huh?

261
00:26:57,077 --> 00:26:58,954
Man, I'm tired.

262
00:27:00,121 --> 00:27:05,001
I think half the people we served
this morning came in just to look at you.

263
00:27:05,085 --> 00:27:07,462
Here you go.

264
00:27:07,545 --> 00:27:10,507
- What's this?
- Your half of the tips.

265
00:27:12,300 --> 00:27:16,387
I thought you said
you were used to being on your feet.

266
00:27:16,471 --> 00:27:20,601
