00:40:01,828 --> 00:40:03,663
- Oh, hey.
- Thought you were sick.

429
00:40:03,747 --> 00:40:06,166
Haven't seen you for a few days.

430
00:40:06,208 --> 00:40:11,465
It's only a two-restaurant town, so I try
to spread the county's money around.

431
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:15,635
Meatloaf. Can I have onion rings
instead of mashed potatoes?

432
00:40:15,677 --> 00:40:18,429
Onion... Sure, I'll ask.

433
00:40:21,557 --> 00:40:23,809
Could you give me a ride home after work?

434
00:40:24,936 --> 00:40:26,354
Sure.

435
00:40:30,025 --> 00:40:32,235
He looks like he's dancing.

436
00:40:32,318 --> 00:40:35,113
Well, maybe just happy to see
a girl with a sack of meat.

437
00:40:35,197 --> 00:40:38,574
I'll give you some here.
Why don't you toss this in?

438
00:40:51,045 --> 00:40:54,757
- He likes the honey.
- I think he does.

439
00:40:54,841 --> 00:40:58,928
Is that really the bear
that hurt Mr. Bradley?

440
00:40:58,969 --> 00:41:01,181
He's the one.

441
00:41:17,447 --> 00:41:19,450
I don't wanna go right home.

442
00:41:19,492 --> 00:41:21,827
- Not just yet.
- You don't?

443
00:41:21,910 --> 00:41:24,288
Can't we just drive a little?

444
00:41:35,007 --> 00:41:38,052
Here's the thing.
I'm gonna be here about three more weeks.

445
00:41:38,135 --> 00:41:40,721
I'm afraid I'm not gonna get through it.

446
00:41:43,224 --> 00:41:45,226
Three weeks, huh?

447
00:41:47,811 --> 00:41:50,355
I don't wanna be in love, Crane.

448
00:42:15,380 --> 00:42:17,049
Don't start without me.

449
00:42:20,302 --> 00:42:23,305
- What's that?
- A flower.

450
00:42:23,346 --> 00:42:25,348
That's not a flower - it's a weed.

451
00:42:28,144 --> 00:42:30,146
It's pretty, though.

452
00:42:30,229 --> 00:42:34,818
- Don't you think it's pretty?
- Yeah, I think it's lovely.

453
00:42:34,860 --> 00:42:37,278
You want to wait a little longer
for your mother?

454
00:42:37,362 --> 00:42:39,739
- Just a little bit.
- OK.

455
00:42:45,286 --> 00:42:47,789
I had a music teacher
who was a lesbian.

456
00:42:55,255 --> 00:42:57,465
You guys are gay, right?

457
00:43:03,346 --> 00:43:07,183
I'd think after 40 years of working together,
one of us would notice, don't you?

458
00:43:07,266 --> 00:43:11,563
Well, Einar, I always thought
you had really lovely hands.

459
00:43:11,646 --> 00:43:14,524
You did? You never told me that.

460
00:43:14,607 --> 00:43:18,110
I mean, it's cool.
Everybody needs love.

461
00:43:18,194 --> 00:43:20,446
You got that part right, little girl.

462
00:43:21,531 --> 00:43:23,741
Jeez, what's next?

463
00:43:24,451 --> 00:43:26,244
Hey!

464
00:43:28,163 --> 00:43:31,833
- Hey, yourself. How you doing?
- Good. How are you?

465
00:43:31,916 --> 00:43:35,545
Good. There's somebody
I want you to meet.

466
00:43:36,796 --> 00:43:39,592
Griff, this is Sheriff Curtis.

467
00:43:39,675 --> 00:43:41,719
Nice to meet you, Griff.

468
00:43:43,178 --> 00:43:46,139
- Are you hungry?
- There isn't enough.

469
00:43:46,223 --> 00:43:50,436
I gotta swing back
through town anyway. So I'll see ya.

470
00:43:50,519 --> 00:43:54,189
- Thanks for the ride home.
- Take care of yourself, Crane.

471
00:43:55,775 --> 00:43:57,735
- I don't like him.
- I don't remember asking.

472
00:43:57,818 --> 00:43:59,820
I don't remember you ever asking me.

473
00:43:59,903 --> 00:44:02,656
Hey, I don't need your permission.

474
00:44:06,076 --> 00:44:09,079
You confused about how
to treat a guest in my house?

475
00:44:09,121 --> 00:44:11,123
It's just some guy my mom brought home.

476
00:44:11,206 --> 00:44:14,918
I expect you to be pleasant
to whoever comes to my door.

477
00:44:19,757 --> 00:44:21,007
Yes, sir.

478
00:44:21,091 --> 00:44:24,469
Unless it's some guy
looking to sell his angle on God.

479
00:44:24,553 --> 00:44:27,639
There's no excuse for that bullshit.

480
00:44:30,559 --> 00:44:36,398
